headline: Corrections & Amplifications
summary: CORRECTIONS Héctor “el Güero” Palma wasn’t extradited to the U.S. In some editions Friday, a U.S. News article about the extradition of imprisoned Mexicans accused of crimes in the U.S. incorrectly said that Palma was in the group.
